query:
SELECT e.id, e.evaluation_date, gp.name as gp_name, gp.team_id, t.name as team_name
FROM evaluations e
JOIN game_presenters gp ON e.game_presenter_id = gp.id
JOIN fm_teams t ON gp.team_id = t.id
WHERE t.name = 'Team Alpha'
ORDER BY e.evaluation_date DESC
LIMIT 10;
